data.description: A very well-maintained eight-room, four-bedroom home situated on 9.96+/- acres of land. The kitchen features granite counter tops, oak cabinets, tile floor and appliances. The dining and spacious living room has beautiful hardwood floors. There are sliding doors leading to a deck in the back yard from the dining room.  Three of the four bedrooms are on the main living floor with the fourth bedroom above the garage. The primary bedroom includes a ¾ bath, with whirlpool tub and larger walk-in closet. The basement has a family room with a Harmen Pellet stove, ½ bath with laundry and large workshop area. There is an attached two car garage, and a detached two car garage for all your storage needs. This home was built by the current owner and pride of ownership shines throughout.
